    "name": "Elevate Wellness Experience",
    "description": "Create a premium website for a boutique fitness studio called “Elevate Studio”.\n\nConcept:\nHigh-end small-group fitness classes with personal coaching.\n\nAudience:\nProfessionals aged 30–50 who value quality and personalized training.\n\nTone:\nPremium, motivational, polished.\n\nMain colors:\n- Deep navy blue\n- Matte black accents\n- Soft gold highlights\n- White backgrounds\n\nGoals:\nDrive class bookings and memberships.\n\nStructure:\n- Hero with aspirational headline\n- Studio philosophy section\n- Class types (strength, mobility, HIIT)\n- Trainer profiles\n- Testimonials\n- Membership options\n- Booking CTA\n- Location & schedule\n\nDesign guidance:\n- Clean and spacious layout\n- Elegant typography\n- High-quality lifestyle imagery\n- Alternate dark and light sections\n- Minimal clutter\n\nCopy guidance:\n- Focus on transformation and personal attention\n- Avoid aggressive “no pain no gain” language\n- Make it feel exclusive but welcoming\n\nMake it look like a premium wellness brand.\nKeep it conversion-focused and realistic.",
